{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT generates not just a single idea but also the main points of the future plot and prototypes of the characters simultaneously.",
    "The holistic answer could be taken for further development and refinement.",
    "This peculiarity of an AI agent's work must be considered while asking the chatbot about the direction of the plot development or the character's features.",
    "A human author should better do it smoothly, like talking to a real person (Figure 2).",
    "It helps to find out more details about the imaginary or real novel's world, making the story sound more complex and deeper."
  ]
}